headline: 5 homebuilder stocks investors should consider
summary: BofA Securities senior equity analyst of US homebuilders and building products, Rafe Jadrosich, shares several of his top stock picks in the homebuilding sector (XHB), which includes Toll Brothers (TOL), Lennar (LEN), NVR (NVR), PulteGroup (PHM), and D.R. Horton (DHI). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination.
